contentfulProduct.seoTitle: Stretch Cotton Twill Girlfriend Chino Pants
contentfulProduct.seoDescription: These stretch cotton twill pants are garment-dyed for the perfect lived-in look. Featuring a flattering cropped length and straight leg, they're soft with a bit of stretch for extra comfort and the perfect fit.
contentfulProduct.title: Stretch Cotton Twill Girlfriend Chino Pants

content.value: These stretch cotton twill chinos are garment-dyed for the perfect lived-in look. Featuring a flattering cropped length and straight leg, they're soft with a bit of stretch for extra comfort and the perfect fit.
Comfort stretch with good recovery and soft handfeel
Inseam: 27.5"
Front Rise: 10", Back Rise: 14" (size 27)
Two front pocket and two back welt pockets
Garment dyed with twill tape ate side seam
Zipper fly and faux horn button front
Belt loops at waistband
Material: 97% Cotton / 3% Elastane
This material is produced in OEKO-TEX® Standard 100 certified mill which ensures that no hazardous substances are present.
Origin: Chennai, India
Model is 5'9" and wearing a size 27
Machine wash cold. Gentle cycle. Do not bleach. Tumble dry low. Cool iron or dry clean if needed.
